title: Black Flag - The First Four Years
description:
BLACK FLAG - THE FIRST FOUR YEARS (mp3 320 Kbps)



The First Four Years was a compilation of early Black Flag songs recorded before Henry Rollins became the band&#039;s vocalist in 1981. Released in 1983 on SST Records, it essentially collects the EPs Nervous Breakdown, Jealous Again, Six Pack, and the single Louie Louie, with a couple of bonus tracks from various artists&#039; albums.
